<section class="guide-panel" data-page="echo">
  <header class="panel-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">Echo</span>
    <h2>Sets et priorit&eacute;s de stats</h2>
  </header>

  <div class="echo-shell">
    <div class="echo-sets">
      <article class="echo-set echo-set--best">
        <div class="echo-set__header">
          <div class="echo-set__title">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Rejuvenating%20Glow.png" alt="&Eacute;clat rajeunissant" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-choice-label">Choix recommand&eacute;</span>
              <h3>&Eacute;clat rajeunissant</h3>
              <p>
                Le set support le plus propre, avec
                <span class="accent-value">+10% bonus de soin</span> et
                <span class="accent-value">+15% ATQ d'&eacute;quipe</span> apr&egrave;s soin.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="echo-item-grid">
          <article class="echo-item echo-item--primary">
            <img src="../../assets/img/echo/Fallacy%20of%20No%20Return.png" alt="X78 - Erreur intarissable" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label echo-item__label--primary">&Eacute;cho recommand&eacute;</span>
              <h4>X78 - Erreur intarissable</h4>
              <p>
                Le meilleur choix standard : ER, buff d'&eacute;quipe et rotation tr&egrave;s stable.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="echo-item echo-item--secondary">
            <img src="../../assets/img/echo/Bell-Borne%20Geochelone.png" alt="Tortue clochante" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label">Alternative d&eacute;fensive</span>
              <h4>Tortue clochante</h4>
              <p>
                Alternative plus s&ucirc;re si tu veux davantage de mitigation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="echo-set echo-set--alt">
        <div class="echo-set__header">
          <div class="echo-set__title">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Moonlit%20Clouds.png" alt="Nuages lunaires" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-choice-label echo-choice-label--alt">Alternative cibl&eacute;e</span>
              <h3>Nuages lunaires</h3>
              <p>
                Plus cibl&eacute;, mais tr&egrave;s propre si tu veux surtout renforcer un carry unique avec
                <span class="accent-value">+22,5% ATQ</span> apr&egrave;s l'Outro.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="echo-item-grid">
          <article class="echo-item">
            <img src="../../assets/img/echo/Impermanence%20Heron.png" alt="H&eacute;ron impermanent" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label">&Eacute;cho associ&eacute;</span>
              <h4>H&eacute;ron impermanent</h4>
              <p>
                &Agrave; jouer si ta team cherche surtout un buff propre sur le carry qui entre.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="echo-mainstats">
      <div class="echo-mainstats__header">
        <span class="echo-mainstats__kicker">Meilleures stats d'&Eacute;cho</span>
        <h3>Configuration 4 / 3 / 3 / 1 / 1</h3>
        <p>
          Commence par verrouiller la Recharge d'&eacute;nergie. Les substats servent ensuite &agrave; lisser les PV et le petit profil offensif.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="echo-mainstats__grid">
        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">4 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">DGT CRIT</span>
            <span class="mainstat-sep">&gt;</span>
            <span class="mainstat-alt">Bonus soin</span>
            <span class="mainstat-sep">&gt;</span>
            <span class="mainstat-alt">PV%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le DGT CRIT rentabilise le mieux son Intro renforc&eacute;e.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card mainstat-card--priority">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">3 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">Recharge d'&eacute;nergie%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Priorit&eacute; absolue pour lancer la Lib&eacute;ration &agrave; chaque rotation.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">3 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">Recharge d'&eacute;nergie%</span>
            <span class="mainstat-sep">&gt;</span>
            <span class="mainstat-alt">PV%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le second 3 co&ucirc;t reste souvent en ER avant de passer sur du PV%.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">1 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">PV%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Ses soins et ses buffs montent naturellement avec les PV.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">1 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">PV%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le duo 1 co&ucirc;t PV% garde le build simple et coh&eacute;rent.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="echo-substats-divider">
        <span>Substats prioritaires</span>
      </div>

      <div class="substats-grid substats-grid--single">
        <article class="substat-card">
          <h4>Ordre recommand&eacute;</h4>
          <p>
            <span class="accent-text">Recharge d'&eacute;nergie</span> jusqu'au palier
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">DGT CRIT</span>
            &gt;= <span class="accent-text">DGT de Lib&eacute;ration%</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">PV%</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">Taux CRIT</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">PV</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">ATQ%</span>
            = <span class="accent-text">ATQ</span>
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>
